OL,6,FThe FTSE 100 is at its lowest level
OL,7,Fsince March after falling by 1.8 per
OL,8,Fcent today.
OL,10,FOf the index's 100 members, 96 have
OL,11,Fseen their share price fall on
OL,12,FWednesday, with just four going up.
OL,14,FIt comes after the Office for
OL,15,FNational Statistics (ONS) announced
OL,16,Fthe rate of Consumer Prices Index
OL,17,F(CPI) inflation decreased to 8.7 per
OL,18,Fcent in April from 10.1 per cent in
OL,19,FMarch.
